
Script use different tools to give informations and to do it job.
It perform some checks so user wont make mistake when formating.

-i or --identify    # Display mounted partitions
Ex.: 
  forma -i

-u or --umount      # Define location to umount
Ex.: 
  forma -u -p /dev/sdb1

-f or --format      # Define type of format. ( ext3, ext4, vfat... )
Ex.: 
  forma -f ext4 -p /dev/sdb1

